11. Ne5 Be7
{ Black's bishop is also not doing much on c5. Therefore this retreat, similarly to our Be2, is pretty normal. }
12. Ndc4 Rxd1+ 13. Bxd1 Nbd7 { Black is protecting the b6-square. } 14. Bd2
