11. Nge2 Nf5 12. Qd2 Re8
{ Black is forcing us to give the d3-bishop, but it is not a problem since we will trade it for a knight and not for the bad c8-bishop. }
13. Bxf5 Bxf5 14. Ng3 Be6 15. O-O
{ With e4-e5 to follow and thanks to the weakened dark squares on the kingside, our attack will have good chances to succeed. }
