{ Our knight on d2 is misplaced, and it looks like a nice plan to bring it over to a4 via Nb1-Bd2-Nc3-Na4 and attack the weakness on b6. In any case, because of our better structure and the pair of bishops, we enjoy a slight but long-lasting advantage. }
