9... Bd6 10. Qe2+ Kf8
{ Again there is no ...Qe7, because of the hanging bishop on d6, so Black has to move their king, which will secure our advantage for the near future. }
11. Be3 { Nf3 and O-O are coming. Black has serious issues with their king. } *

