{ This is the Baltic Defence, a pretty rare opening which has the strange idea of fighting for the centre by taking a knight on b1! }
3. cxd5 Qxd5
{ This is just very bad, and completely not in the spirit of the opening. } 4.
Nc3 { Now the queen has to go and the bishop is doing nothing on f5. } 4... Qd8
