{ With this move order Black keeps the possibility of castling long, which is traditionally the main concept of this variation. }
9. Nf3 Bc5 10. a3
{ A very-very promising new line, instead of the much more popular and heavily analysed main line  10.e3  . The idea is to control the b4-square and therefore make Bg5 possible.  10.Bg5?!  is not yet possible due to  10...Qb6!  11.e3  Qxb2  12.Bxf6  gxf6  13.Nd5  Bf5  and Black has a good position. }
