{ The only try for the advantage. We keep Black busy with their bishop. } 5...
Nc6
{ The most natural developing move. Black is still keeping their options: they can play with ...Bxc5 later as well, but they don't give up on the ...Ne4 idea either.   The immediate  5...Bxc5  is possible, but it will transpose after  6.Nf3  with either  Nc6  7.Bg5  or  @@StartFEN@@rnbqk2r/pp1p1ppp/4pn2/2b5/2P5/1QN2N2/PP2PPPP/R1B1KB1R b KQkq - 1 6@@EndFEN@@  6...O-O  7.Bg5  when eventually Black will play ...Nc6. }
