11. O-O-O h5
{ The position after  11...Kh7  12.g4  is analysed in the 6...Nbd7 line, after  @@StartFEN@@r1bq1rk1/pppnppbp/3p1np1/6B1/2PPP3/2N5/PP2BPPP/R2QK1NR w KQ - 4 7@@EndFEN@@  7.Qd2  e5  8.d5  Nc5  9.f3  h6  10.Be3  a5  11.O-O-O  Kh7  12.g4  . }
12. h4
