13... a6 { The gameAtalik-Pap features  13...Qb6  . } 14. a4 Qa5 15. Qc2
{ So we can meet  15...Qb4  with  16.b3  . } 15... h6 16. Bd2
{ Now the seemingly active queen has to retreat. } 16... Qc7 17. Rae1 Rxe1 18.
Rxe1 Re8 19. Rxe8+ Nxe8 20. b3
{ The next step is to place our queen on the e-file and let Black decide whether to exchange it or remain passive with their queen instead. }
