{ Exactly like this! Absolutely coherent with our philosophy in this opening, we give Black as little counterplay as possible.   After  9.cxd5  there is  9...Re8  to attack e4 @@StartBracket@@counterplay Nr.1@@EndBracket@@ and on  10.f3  a6  , using the queenside majority. @@StartBracket@@counterplay Nr.2@@EndBracket@@ }
