3... d6
{ Instead,  3...f5  4.e4!  and the best Black has is to play  4...d6  and transpose to a bad version of the 3...d6 variation.  4...Nf6  is much worse:  5.exf5!  and we can simply keep our extra pawn.  5...d6  6.g4  h5  7.g5  Ng8  8.Bh3+-  . }
