Qf6 13. Bf4
{ According to the computer,  13.Nd2!  is the best but, for me, this move is simply much easier. }
13... Qxc3
{ Black is taking the pawn, but they can't keep this extra pawn for long. } 14.
Rfc1 Qxd3 15. exd3 Nf6 16. Rxc5
{ White is much better in the endgame. Black has serious issues to finish development. }
