{ A double attack which is very easy to meet.  6...Bxd6  is basically the same:  7.Bxd6  cxd6  8.e3  O-O  9.Be2  Be6  10.O-O+-  and Black is down a pawn for no compensation. }
7. Qd2 Bxd6 8. Bxd6 cxd6 9. Nc3 { White is up a pawn with a better structure. }
