7. Ne4
{ Gaining the pair of bishops, since after  7...Bb4+  8.Bd2  and the eventual bishop trade, Nd6+ is coming. }
7... Nxe5 8. Nxc5 Qxc5 9. Bd2
{ Black has weak dark squares. Moreover, normal development is not possible because of the c6-pawn. White has a clear advantage with the pair of bishops. }
