7. Bxd6 cxd6 8. Nb5 Ne4 9. Ne2 { Preparing f3, so we can meet Qh4+ with g3. }
9... a6 10. Nbc3 O-O 11. d5
{ Black's structure is worse, and they will have serious issues with queenside development. }
