{ Preventing g4-ideas from White, but for a potential bishop endgame it is not really good to fix the pawns on light squares. Of course, that is still very far away. }
21. Rd1 Rfd8 22. Rd2
{ I would have already played  22.h4!?  now, but Eljanov decided to wait with it. }
22... Kf8 23. Rfd1 Ke7 24. Bb1
